General.Name: Antilia Group Corp
General.Description: Antilia Group, Corp. engages in the development of applications (apps) and games. It develops Android and iOS apps and games. The company was founded in 2016 and is based in Sosua, Dominican Republic. Antilia Group, Corp. operates as a subsidiary of Greenwich Holdings Ltd.
General.Address: Calle Duarte, No. 6, Sosua, Dominican Republic
